 Water Intake Tracker

A simple Python project to track daily water consumption.  
Users can set a daily goal, log their intake, and view progress reports.

 Features
Set daily water intake goal
Log water intake (ml)
See total, remaining amount, and completion %
Automatically saves logs
Simple CLI interface

 Technologies Used
 Python 3

 Files
 main.py — main program
 water_log.txt — stored data

